desc_short	-----								Watch an object obediently melt, mold and bend in your hands. Map up your room to work on physical desks and tables. Artists can sculpt high quality models with little or no instruction. Models are saved as .obj, for easy use in Unity, Unreal Engine, ZBrush, Blender and so on.							
